kuiq -- The micro-vlogging application

By leveraging the Youtube API, kuiq delivers a web application inspired by
Twitter, the worlds most successful micro-blogging platform, to introduce the
world to micro-vlogging.

All videos displayed publicly on kuiq are 30seconds or less and descriptions are
limited to 140 characters.

kuiq is written with Ruby On Rails and is FOSS. Anyone may copy, modify, port
to other languages, and distribute kuiq code as long as attribution is given
to the original author: Justin Mancinelli.

